name: FindmeBreakfast
0:
”Alexa, open Find me Breakfast.”
”What is the closest breakfast place to me?”
”Find me a diner.”
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.

Developer Terms of Use
des: Locate the closest 24 hour diner near you to enjoy a meal at any time of day. Allow Find me Breakfast to use your device zip code to locate the closest diner near you.
